<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
    <title>Farmers-Choice</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        html {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-size: 62.5%;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
            background-color: rgba(72, 201, 176, 0.6);
        }


        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .card-body {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .card-footer {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .review {
            width: 85%;
            margin: auto;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            top: 1rem;
        }

        .reviewsSection {
            width: 90%;
            margin: auto;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 2rem;
        }

        img {
            width: 350px;
            height: 250px;
        }

        .images {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-content: center;
            margin: auto;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="reviewsSection">
        <h1 class="text-center">Welcome to Farmers Choice!</h1>
        <p class="text-center">The first of its kind. This website allows you to view and order produce sold by farmers around Kenya. It also allows you to post produce to be sole on the website if you are a farmer.</p>

        <hr>
        <h3 class="text-center">Other buyers reviews!</h3>

        <div class="review">
            <div class="card-body">"Exquisite and high quality produce assured, you will not be disappointed!"</div>
            <div class="card-footer"><em>From: </em>User5421</div>
        </div>
        <div class="review">
            <div class="card-body">"Produce is delivered very quickly to wherever you are."</div>
            <div class="card-footer"><em>From: </em>User4336</div>
        </div>
        <div class="review">
            <div class="card-body">"Got exactly what I ordered for in exactly the right quantity, that's rare!"</div>
            <div class="card-footer"><em>From: </em>User1190</div>
        </div>
        <div class="review">
            <div class="card-body">"Surprised I got almost everything I needed from here..."</div>
            <div class="card-footer"><em>From: </em>User3321</div>
        </div>
        <div class="review">
            <div class="card-body">"Amazing variety"</div>
            <div class="card-footer"><em>From: </em>User7775</div>
        </div>
        <div class="review">
            <div class="card-body">"Prices are very reasonable and affordable for almost everybody with an internet connection and means of online payment"</div>
            <div class="card-footer"><em>From: </em>User0965</div>
        </div>
        <div class="review">
            <div class="card-body">"Remarkably fresh vegetables for me to enjoy tonight. Yummmmm"</div>
            <div class="card-footer"><em>From: </em>User1215</div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <br>
        <h1 class="text-center image-heading">View just some produce our farmers sell.</h1>
        <br>
        <div class="images">
            <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/sxvRcnrb/fish.jpg" class="display-photos" alt="display-photos" />
            <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/63QsWHyT/fruits-and-vegetables.jpg" class="display-photos" alt="display-photos" />
            <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/x1VWJjcw/meat.jpg" class="display-photos" alt="display-photos" />
            <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/mrbJjd3V/more-vegetables.jpg" class="display-photos" alt="display-photos" />
            <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/W3yy2TBf/pineapples.jpg" class="display-photos" alt="display-photos" />
            <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/sxZNxbyf/vegetables.jpg" class="display-photos" alt="display-photos" />
        </div>


    </div>

</body>